Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.82,0:00:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Jesus said that the identifying mark
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.61,0:00:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,of true Christians would be
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.61,0:00:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,their love for one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.62,0:00:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,This was especially evident
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.53,0:00:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,at our 2019 “Love Never Fails”!\NInternational Conventions.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.71,0:00:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I never expected\Nthe welcome that we received.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.76,0:00:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,There were over 200 brothers in the airport.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.43,0:00:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,For me, it’s like I’m in Paradise already\Nbecause of the love I feel here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.23,0:00:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Wherever I turn, there’s love.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.73,0:00:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,As I walked around the corner,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.23,0:00:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,the reception of the friends,\Nthe way they embraced me,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.90,0:00:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,was something\Nthat I could not have expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.86,0:00:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,No one could’ve even described it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.50,0:01:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Mexico has a lot of different cultures.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.92,0:01:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But here in this stadium,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.92,0:01:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,we are one people united by love,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.30,0:01:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,serving Jehovah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.30,0:01:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s unique, it’s wonderful,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.10,0:01:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and it’s all thanks to love.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.18,0:01:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn’t matter where we come from\Nor what language we speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.06,0:01:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The language here is love.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.74,0:01:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Our love of neighbor motivated us\Nto share in a global preaching campaign.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.91,0:01:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Foreign delegates\Nworked shoulder to shoulder
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.04,0:01:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,with hosts from the local city
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.04,0:01:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,to invite millions of people\Nfrom around the world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.00,0:01:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,to one of the 24 international conventions.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.80,0:01:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This gave our brothers and sisters\Nfrom different parts of the globe
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.80,0:01:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,an opportunity to get to know each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.68,0:02:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,united by the common goal of spreading\Nthe good news to everyone they met.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.85,0:02:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I worked in field service with a sister
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.85,0:02:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,who used to study the Bible\Nwith a Brazilian woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.90,0:02:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The sister had prayed to send\Na Brazilian sister to accompany her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.44,0:02:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,When we visited the woman together,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.95,0:02:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,she could see the love we have between us
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.70,0:02:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,and the efforts we made to come so far
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.33,0:02:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,to attend the convention here in Denmark.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.95,0:02:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Over a million people attended
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.75,0:02:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,the international conventions\Nin many different languages.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.25,0:02:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Both foreign and local delegates\Nas well as newly interested ones
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.92,0:02:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,were able to learn firsthand\Nhow love never fails.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.93,0:02:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,“Clothe yourselves with love,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.31,0:02:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,for it is a perfect bond of union.”
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.73,0:02:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,First, love identifies us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.11,0:02:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Humility\N—that’s love in action.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.49,0:02:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Loyal love is a beautiful aspect
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.16,0:02:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,of Jehovah’s personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.49,0:03:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Jesus made it simple, didn’t he?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.62,0:03:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,He said: ‘Look for the love.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.16,0:03:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Look for the love,\Nand you’ll find the right religion.’
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.25,0:03:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Christian love has power.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.55,0:03:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It can reach hearts in ways
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.09,0:03:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,that the spoken word cannot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.14,0:03:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But, really,\Nwhat other group of persons on earth
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.14,0:03:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,are interested in discussing\Nlove that doesn’t fail?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.56,0:03:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,When someone sees us,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.56,0:03:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,they should see a loving individual.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.07,0:03:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,When they see any one of us
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.11,0:03:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,who are servants of Jehovah,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.15,0:03:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,then they should see love.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.62,0:03:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,In addition to spending time in the ministry,\Nactivities were planned
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.71,0:03:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,so that delegates could get to know
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.13,0:03:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,their brothers better.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.30,0:04:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This gave delegates the opportunity\Nto learn about the culture
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.26,0:04:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and our spiritual heritage\Nin the host country.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.14,0:04:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,In some cities,\Nthey visited exhibits and locations
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.48,0:04:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,where previously our faith\Nand love had been tested.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.11,0:04:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,For example, delegates in Berlin\Nhad the opportunity to visit
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.99,0:04:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Sachsenhausen concentration camp
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.32,0:04:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,where many of our brothers were imprisoned
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.74,0:04:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,during World War II.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.37,0:04:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it was especially amazing,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.37,0:04:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,despite the circumstances\Nthose brothers and sisters faced,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.84,0:04:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,that even their persecutors
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.88,0:04:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,had to recognize\Nthe true identifying mark of Christianity
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.97,0:04:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,—of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.47,0:04:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This visit showed the faithful endurance\Nour brothers and sisters
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.10,0:04:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,demonstrated under vicious persecution
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.06,0:04:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and the love they had for Jehovah
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.02,0:04:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,–a fitting example of love that never fails.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.11,0:05:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Adolf Hitler wanted to exterminate\NJehovah’s Witnesses;
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.74,0:05:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,he called them a brood.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.37,0:05:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But instead,\NJehovah’s Witnesses are still here,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.66,0:05:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,proving that Christian love never fails.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.09,0:05:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Another example of faith and endurance\Nwas seen in Seoul, Korea.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.59,0:05:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Since 1953,\Nyoung Korean brothers had been imprisoned
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.43,0:05:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,for refusing military service.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.68,0:05:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Altogether,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.73,0:05:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,over 19,000 brothers\Nwho refused to compromise their faith
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.27,0:05:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,spent nearly 37,000 years in prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.90,0:05:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Delegates were able to visit\Na neutrality exhibition to learn more
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.62,0:05:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,about the strong faith and unwavering courage
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.20,0:05:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,these young brothers displayed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.41,0:05:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,On February 28, 2019,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.54,0:05:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,the last of our imprisoned brothers\Nwas released.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.01,0:06:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I received\Na not-guilty verdict just two weeks ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.72,0:06:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I was able to attend\Nthis international convention.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.89,0:06:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I am so grateful to Jehovah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.56,0:06:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,My son receiving this acquittal\Nenabled him to attend this convention.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.44,0:06:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We never imagined this would be possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.69,0:06:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What a joy it was\Nfor these brothers to attend
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.82,0:06:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,this historic international convention\Nalongside their families
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.24,0:06:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and thousands of foreign delegates!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.29,0:06:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Just being able to sit\Nnext to my son for the convention
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.87,0:06:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,completely fills my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.85,0:06:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Despite an ongoing economic crisis,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.18,0:06:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,many delegates from Venezuela
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.43,0:06:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,were able to attend\Nthe international convention
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.19,0:06:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,in Sao Paulo, Brazil.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.44,0:07:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming from Venezuela,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.48,0:07:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,it’s difficult to earn\Na living or save money.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.70,0:07:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We had to sell our electronic devices\Nand work long hours to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.16,0:07:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But these sacrifices
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.20,0:07:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,will always be worth it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.13,0:07:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The love we show to our brothers is possible
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.71,0:07:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,because of the love Jehovah shows us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.17,0:07:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,An expression of his love to us\Ncomes in the form of his Word, the Bible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.80,0:07:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,In Copenhagen, Denmark,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.81,0:07:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,delegates from Iceland\Nwere delighted to receive a special gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.64,0:07:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We are happy to announce the release
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.94,0:07:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,of the Icelandic {\i1}{\fs18}{\fnSerif}New World Translation {\r}\N{\i1}{\fs18}{\fnSerif}of the Christian Greek Scriptures.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.95,0:07:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Additionally,\Nat several 2019 international conventions,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.96,0:08:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,our brothers received\Nthe revised {\i1}{\fs18}{\fnSerif}New World Translation 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.29,0:08:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,in the language of their heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.04,0:08:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I can really feel the love from Jehovah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.71,0:08:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,He’s given us this wonderful gift
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.04,0:08:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,because he wants us to know\Nthat the words in this book
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.34,0:08:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,are from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.47,0:08:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The conventions also gave\Nthousands the opportunity
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.51,0:08:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,to express their love for Jehovah
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.60,0:08:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,by symbolizing their dedication to him
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.56,0:08:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,through baptism.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.23,0:09:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The love among our brothers\Nwas evident to onlookers as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.82,0:09:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The police directing traffic
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.82,0:09:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,had less work than they normally do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.07,0:09:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The atmosphere was so contagious\Nthat they started greeting
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.99,0:09:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,foreign and local delegates.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.08,0:09:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,They were so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.21,0:09:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,They said:\N“This country does not need more police.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.29,0:09:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What it needs is more Jehovah’s Witnesses!”
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.59,0:09:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Our 2019 international conventions\Nhave given us
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.39,0:09:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,an opportunity to demonstrate\Nhow Jehovah’s love
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.39,0:09:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,motivates us to love.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.64,0:09:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, as we approach\Nthe end of this system of things,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.90,0:09:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,we’re going to need love\Nmore than ever before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.90,0:09:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course,\Nwe need loyalty;
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.19,0:09:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,of course,\Nwe need endurance;
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.36,0:09:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,and, of course,\Nwe’re going to sing that song of courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.49,0:09:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But remember what else we want
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.54,0:10:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,—Jehovah’s loyal love!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.79,0:10:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,May we be determined\Nto imitate Him in letting
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.79,0:10:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,our love never ever fail,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.97,0:10:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,all to Jehovah’s glory.
